Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.60,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}『Thank you, my twilight』— the Pillows
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.95,0:00:21.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,世界必须先被毁灭 之后才能变得美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:21.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The world must be destroyed before it can become beautiful.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.60,0:00:22.80,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Life, Life is beautiful
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.60,0:00:22.80,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}生命，生命如此美丽
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.55,0:00:24.42,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这是我在心中描绘的世界的愿景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:24.42,Line EN,,0,0,0,,This is the world I envisioned.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.34,0:00:29.45,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕のルーレット　回り続けてる
Dialogue: 2,0:00:23.34,0:00:29.45,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我的轮盘 会一直转动下去
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.39,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这是世界应有的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.39,Line EN,,0,0,0,,This is how the world should be.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但在这个世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But in this world,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.82,0:00:32.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,只有我的身体在腐烂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:32.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,only my body is rotting --
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.02,0:00:35.31,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}She, She is wonderful
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.02,0:00:35.31,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}她，她是这般美妙
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.19,0:00:34.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,渐渐朽坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:34.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,becoming decayed.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.33,Line CN,,0,0,0,,没错 它正在朽坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.33,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Yes, decaying.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.31,0:00:42.06,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}その瞳に今を映したい
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.31,0:00:42.06,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}想要让她的眼睛 映照出现在
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.33,0:00:41.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也许这是我原本该有的样貌{PV原文: これが私のあるべき姿だったんのかもしれない}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:41.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is how my body should have been.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.44,0:00:49.54,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也许这才是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:49.54,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is my true self.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.02,0:00:47.56,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}迷わないでもぎ取った予感を
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.02,0:00:47.56,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}毫不犹豫抓住的预感
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.61,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但我最后还是想起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.61,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But then finally, I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.54,0:00:56.54,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誰かと待ち合わせてるみたいに
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.54,0:00:56.54,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}好像在等待着谁似的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.61,0:00:56.28,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我还只是一个初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:56.28,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that I'm still only a junior high student,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我并没思考过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that I wasn't thinking about anything,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.54,0:01:02.18,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}見えたなら間違いじゃない
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.54,0:01:02.18,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果看到就肯定不会有错
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,还有 这里从不曾发生什么了不起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and that nothing amazing has ever happened here.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,一切都是那么平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Everything is ordinary.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.37,0:01:07.78,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミを待ってたんだ
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.37,0:01:07.78,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一直在等你
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.76,0:01:23.20,Insert JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}She, She is wonderful
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.76,0:01:23.20,Insert CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}她，她是这般美妙
